Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.45,Sign 1,,0,0,0,,{\move(937.5,6,937.5,613.5)}Mực
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thường thì làm kẻ săn mồi đó...
